Here's a full version of the Node.js API with realistic features:

*bigi-api.js*
```
```

This API includes the following features:

- CORS support for cross-origin requests
- API endpoint to get product details by name
- API endpoint to update product details
- API endpoint to get all products
- API endpoint to handle orders
- API endpoint to get order receipt

Note that you should replace the database credentials and table names with your own.

Also, make sure to test the API using tools like Postman or cURL.